{
  "texts": [
    "Table 3: Embeddings to edit effect to performance of CHAMELEON.",
    "To examine the impact of the amount of user history data on performance, we run CHAMELEON on the LaMP2 and LaMP3 task, varying the number of history per user as {5, 10, 15, 20, 25}, while keeping the number of users in the group constant.",
    "Figure 5 illustrates that when the amount of user history data is small, the performance improvement of CHAMELEON is limited.",
    "This limitation likely arises from the difficulty in generating accurate personalization insights with insufficient data.",
    "Conversely, when the amount of history data is too big, the performance of CHAMELEON declines."
  ]
}